unwound.title: ‘Pizza to the Polls’ sends free food to people waiting in long lines to vote
unwound.description: A non-profit group called “Pizza to the Polls” is delivering hundreds of pizzas to voters stuck in long lines waiting to vote.The donation-based website accepts pizza requests from anywhere in the U.S.
